meta.content: Thank you for your interest in the Vernon Independent School District. We are very proud of the services we provide our children. Vernon ISD personnel are committed to providing an educational opportunity that prepares our students to compete in a technology rich society that will continue to evolve the next step in their educational journey.

p.span: Governor Abbott has just issued an Executive Order that requires School Closures and Remote instruction to remain in place through May 4th. He has defined Essential Services and my understanding is nothing will change in the way we are currently operating our district. We will continue to have meals delivered to bus stops, as well as, the lines at the VHS campus. Packets will still go out on Mondays, and we will continue to monitor and adjust copies to be available each day of the week. We are asking that work be submitted online and packets be returned on each Friday.
Thank you for you patience and understanding with this matter!
